# Stats

This is a markdown template to embed the stats generated by `gh-stats`.

## User
These stats are for user [{{.User}}](https://github.com/{{.User}}).

## General stats
| Kind | Number |
| ---- | ------ |
| Repos | {{.NumRepos}} |
| Forks | {{.NumForks}} |
| Pulls | {{.NumPulls}} |
| Commits | {{.NumCommits}} |
| Reviews | {{.NumReviews}} |

## Language stats
| Language | Used (%) |
| -------- | -------- |
{{- range .Languages }}
| {{.Name}} | {{printf "%.2f" .Perc}}% |
{{- end }}

## Extras
You can render extra annotations taken from a json file, like for example the following extras:
| Key | Value |
| --- | ----- |
| `key1` | {{index .Extras "key1"}} |
| `key2` | {{index .Extras "key2"}} |

An extra can have a nested object too! The value of the nested object is: '{{index (index .Extras "object") "value"}}'.
